      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently not in reliable running order. The exterior suffers from significant structural rust, particularly along the rocker panels and wheel wells, along with various dents and clear coat failure. Mechanically, the engine requires a major overhaul due to a persistent head gasket issue, and the transmission shifts harshly between gears. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. This would be an ideal project for a dedicated mechanic or a source for salvageable parts.",
