    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering high-revving performance through its six individual throttle bodies and precise 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis remains composed thanks to refreshed bushings and a reinforced rear subframe, mitigating common floor pan fatigue. Equipped with the factory limited-slip differential and a responsive steering rack, this example offers a visceral analog driving experience. Recent maintenance includes a VANOS overhaul and valve adjustment, ensuring the high-pressure system operates within factory tolerances. The exterior retains its athletic stance with flared arches and staggered Style 67 wheels. A driver-focused cockpit with minimal bolster wear makes this a prime candidate for the discerning enthusiast seeking mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
