      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This vehicle has been exceptionally well-maintained and serves as a testament to responsible ownership. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin remains a refined space; the leather upholstery is clean and supple, with only light creasing on the driver's side bolster. All electronic components, including the infotainment system, heated seats, and driver-assist features, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine. I possess a comprehensive folder of service records, including a recent professional detailing and a fresh oil change. The tires have significant tread life remaining, and the brakes feel firm and confident. This is a solid, honest car that offers a premium experience for its next owner.",
